#

Simple Pasta Primavera

25 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

PastaVegetarianQuick Meal

Description

A vibrant and colorful pasta dish packed with fresh vegetables, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pasta (your choice): 8 oz
  • bell peppers (mixed colors): 1 cup, sliced
  • zucchini: 1 medium, sliced
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
